        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【新加坡直擊】POCO 發佈 F7 Ultra，旗下首部 Ultra 機款 + 定價超抵玩 + 同場加映 F7 Pro</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/poco-launch-first-ultra-phone-in-singapore-with-f7pro/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=poco-launch-first-ultra-phone-in-singapore-with-f7pro</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/poco-launch-first-ultra-phone-in-singapore-with-f7pro/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 10:09:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[F7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[F7 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[F7 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Poco]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299618</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日下午，小米旗下的子品牌 POCO 就在新加坡發佈了新一代的旗艦機款 F7 系列，當中除了預期之內的 F7 Pro 外，還首次推出旗下首部 Ultra 機款：POCO F7 Ultra。現在就讓 Edward 帶大家到現場，看看這兩部手機有甚麼特別吧。</p><h2>POCO F7 系列 = Redmi K80 系列變奏版</h2><p>今次 POCO 發佈的兩部全新 F7 系列手機，分別是 F7 Pro 及 F7 Ultra，其實他們本身就是去年小米在中國發佈的 Redmi K80 及 K80 Pro 的變奏版，所以大體設計上及規格上都十分相似。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02624-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02624-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02624.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>F7 Ultra 首次引入長焦鏡</h2><p>先説今次兩部新機較高階的一部：POCO F7 Ultra，它屬於旗艦級數機款，配備了最新 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite 處理器、12GB / 16GB LPDDR5X RAM 及 256GB / 512GB UFS 4.1 內存，亦內建了 6.67 吋 2K 解析度 120Hz 更新率 Flow AMOLED 熒幕，所以整體配置上均與現時市場上的旗艦手機分別不大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02630-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02630-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02630.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02471-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02471-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02471.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02472-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02472-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02472.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而它既然説得上 Ultra，自然擁有最強硬件，最明顯就是強化了相機配置，除了內建採用 Light Fusion 800 感光元件的 5,000 萬像素主攝鏡及擁有 120 度 FOV 的 3,200 萬像素超廣角鏡外，更首次將長焦鏡引入到 POCO 旗艦機上，而且規格亦達到 5,000 萬像素 2.5x 光學變焦，令 POCO F7 Ultra 不只打機上表現理想，相機成像亦可與市場上的旗艦手機媲美，使用家終於可以「魚與熊掌兼得」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02641.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02652-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02652-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02652.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02561-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02561-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02561.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>散熱方面，POCO F7 Ultra 依然內建了 LiquidCool 4.0 技術，它內建了立體雙通道 IceLoop 散熱系統及大達 5400mm² 超大導熱管，令硬件可進一步下降 3 度。加上它首次內建了 WildBoost Optimization 4.0 技術，利用 AI 自動按需要調節硬件需求，令用家即使玩對圖像處理要求較高的遊戲時，依然有十分理想的效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02378-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02378-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02378.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02483-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02483-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02483.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>官方表示有了這項技術後，觸控反應可有 12% 的提升，而追蹤反應亦可最多提升 22%。官方更表示即使以 2K 120fps 設定運作如《原神》這類遊戲，亦可長時間維持在高水平的幀率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02732-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02732-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02732.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02752-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02752-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02752.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>至於電量方面，POCO F7 Ultra 亦內建了 5,300mAh 容量電池，足夠用家用上一日以上，它亦支援 120W 有線快充及 50W 無線快充，即使回電亦十分快。當然，它亦支援 IP68 防水防塵功能，令用家使用上更加安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02589-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02589-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02589.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
