        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ChatGPT 4o 圖像生成「比預期受歡迎」，OpenAI 延遲開放予免費用戶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/gpt4o-image-generation/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gpt4o-image-generation</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/gpt4o-image-generation/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 09:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4o]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299668</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OpenAI 最新推出的 GPT-4o 圖像生成功能自亮相以來，因需求遠超預期，OpenAI 宣佈暫緩向免費用戶開放此服務。行政總裁 Sam Altman 表示，這項功能在 ChatGPT 的受歡迎程度超出想像，目前僅限付費用戶使用。該技術讓用戶可上傳及修改圖像，並以文字提示精準生成圖片。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">images in chatgpt are wayyyy more popular than we expected (and we had pretty high expectations).</p><p>rollout to our free tier is unfortunately going to be delayed for awhile.</p><p>— Sam Altman (@sama) <a href="https://twitter.com/sama/status/1905000759336620238?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>GPT-4o 圖像生成技術於 3 月 25 日正式推出，允許用戶透過文字指令生成或編輯圖像，並能保持角色風格一致，應用範圍涵蓋設計、藝術創作等。據外媒報道，此功能推出後迅速掀起熱潮，例如在 X 平台上，不少用戶將日常場景或迷因轉化為吉卜力動畫風格，引發廣泛討論。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Today is a great internet day <a href="https://t.co/iPWl2yfvdq">pic.twitter.com/iPWl2yfvdq</a></p><p>— Zeneca.xyz 🔮 (@Zeneca) <a href="https://twitter.com/Zeneca/status/1904774204769411196?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此技術有別於過往依賴 DALL-E 的圖像生成方式，直接建基於 GPT-4o，強調精準度和上下文理解，所有生成圖像均附 C2PA 元數據以標示 AI 來源。OpenAI 同時設限，禁止生成違規內容如 Deepfake 或不當圖像。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">※ワンポチで漫畫が描ける最強 AI</p><p>GPT-4oの畫像生成なら、指定したキャラクターでも漫畫が描けます！</p><p>絵心が壊滅な私でもこのクオリティ！ <a href="https://t.co/qAAgqAiaVY">https://t.co/qAAgqAiaVY</a><a href="https://t.co/DWBFrPIlVX">pic.twitter.com/DWBFrPIlVX</a></p><p>— 結パパ｜AIクリエイター (@Yuupapa_free) <a href="https://twitter.com/Yuupapa_free/status/1904702943095582802?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>OpenAI 近年屢因運算資源不足影響產品推展，例如去年 12 月 Sora 推出後曾暫停新用戶註冊。此次延遲亦被歸咎於相同問題。為解決困境，公司正推進耗資 5,000 億美元（約港幣 3.8 萬億元）的 Stargate 數據中心計畫，預計大幅提升 AI 運算能力。</p><p>GPT-4o 圖像生成功能的熱潮顯示 AI 技術在創意領域的潛力，惟運算資源不足仍是 OpenAI 的挑戰。隨著 Stargate 計畫推進，預計未來數月內免費用戶有望體驗此功能，而技術的持續優化或將進一步擴展其應用場景，值得關注。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2025/03/26/chatgpts-new-ai-image-feature-is-delayed-for-free-users/">Tech Crunch</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/gpt4o-image-generation/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>SNK《餓狼傳説》加入足球巨星 C 朗，非僅宣傳而是可操控角色、絕招用足球踢對手</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 08:05:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SNK]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[餓狼傳説]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299654</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本老牌格鬥遊戲公司 SNK 宣佈，足球巨星 Cristiano Ronaldo （C 朗）將登場《餓狼傳説 City of the Wolves》。遊戲預計於 4 月 24 日在 PlayStation 4、PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X/S 及 PC 平台推出。外界推測，這次跨界合作或與 C 朗效力沙地阿拉伯艾納斯及 SNK 隸屬沙地王儲 MiSK 基金會有關。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032733455-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032733455-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032733455.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SNK 這次將 C 朗引入《餓狼傳説 City of the Wolves》，可謂一大創舉。C 朗作為享譽全球的足球明星，曾效力多隊頂尖球會，並在葡萄牙國家隊擔當核心角色。據網上分析，其加入遊戲的契機與他自 2023 年起在沙地阿拉伯艾納斯密切相關，而 SNK 現由沙國王儲主導的 MiSK 基金會持有，兩者關係促成這場別開生面的合作。官方介紹指，C 朗在遊戲中以足球為基礎設計招式，展現獨特格鬥風格，讓玩家耳目一新。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《餓狼傳説 City of the Wolves》是該系列睽違近 25 年的新作，除保留經典角色如不知火舞外，還加入《Street Fighter》的春麗和 Ken 等跨界角色。C 朗的實機戰鬥畫面已於 3 月 27 日公開，展示他以足球結合武術的創新打法。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_32885"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fbeEWm4_qeg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.inside.com.tw/article/37971-cristiano-ronaldo-fatal-fury-city-of-the-wolves-snk">Inside</a>、<a href="https://www.polygon.com/news/547300/cristiano-ronaldo-fatal-fury-city-of-the-wolves-snk">Polygon</a>、<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E7%8E%8B%E5%87%BA%E7%B5%95%E6%8B%9B%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8A%E9%A4%93%E7%8B%BC%E5%82%B3%E8%AA%AA-cow%E3%80%8B%E7%AB%9F%E6%8A%8A%E3%80%8Cc%E7%BE%85%E3%80%8D%E5%81%9A%E9%80%B2%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%EF%BC%8C%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%94%A8%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-055245650.html">Yahoo</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves/game-channel/">SNK《餓狼傳説》加入足球巨星 C 朗，非僅宣傳而是可操控角色、絕招用足球踢對手</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
